                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for capturing carbon dioxide and preparing methane through in-situ hydrogenation based on eutectic solvent",
                    "一种基于低共熔溶剂的二氧化碳捕集及原位加氢制备甲烷的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a method for capturing carbon dioxide and preparing methane through in-situ hydrogenation based on a deep eutectic solvent, and belongs to the technical field of carbon capturing and utilization. The method comprises the following steps: heating and stirring a hydrogen bond acceptor and ethylene glycol to form a eutectic solvent, capturing carbon dioxide in flue gas by using the eutectic solvent, and then transferring the carbon dioxide into a high-pressure reaction kettle; adding a solid catalyst into the high-pressure reaction kettle, and sealing the reaction kettle; introducing hydrogen into the kettle, and raising the temperature to perform hydrogenation on the captured carbon dioxide to prepare methane; and after the reaction is finished, collecting a gas-phase product, filtering and separating a solid-liquid mixture, and reusing the absorbent and the catalyst. According to the method, after carbon dioxide in the flue gas is captured, in-situ hydrogenation is directly carried out in the absorbent to prepare methane, so that the problems of high energy consumption in the desorption process, high reaction temperature, easy catalyst inactivation and the like in the traditional process of preparing methane through carbon dioxide hydrogenation are solved, the method is simple in process, and the absorbent can be regenerated."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种基于低共熔溶剂的二氧化碳捕集及原位加氢制备甲烷的方法，属于碳捕集利用技术领域。该方法为将氢键受体和乙二醇加热搅拌形成低共熔溶剂，用该低共熔溶剂捕集烟气中的二氧化碳，然后将其转移到高压反应釜内；向高压反应釜内加入固体催化剂，密闭反应釜；再向釜内充入氢气，升高温度对捕集的二氧化碳进行加氢制备甲烷；反应结束后收集气相产物，固液混合物过滤分离，吸收剂和催化剂重复使用。本发明将烟气中的二氧化碳捕集后，直接在吸收剂中原位加氢制备甲烷，避免了解吸过程能耗大和传统二氧化碳加氢制甲烷反应温度高、催化剂易失活等问题，且该法流程简单，吸收剂能够再生。"
                }
            ]
